text: Alexina is a female given name. Notable people with the name include: *Alexina Duchamp (1906–1995), American art dealer *Alexina Graham (born 1990), English fashion model *Alexina Louie (born 1949), Canadian composer *Alexina Ruthquist (1848–1892), Scottish missionary *Alexina Maude Wildman (1867–1896), Australian journalist ==See also== *The Mystery of Alexina, a 1985 French film Category:Feminine given names
